title: The Boys
description: Here it is guys... "The Boy's" Issues 1-23 all wrapped up in one nice little torrent. I am not the one who did the scans, just compiled them altogether, because I had a hell of a time trying to get em ( I Just started reading the comics.) This will bring you as up to date as you can be right now, the new one doesnt come out until november... It's really important that you guys please seed when you are done downloading, don't be a dirty douche mouth! Help keep the community running!
